OL,3,CReport finds no evidence of a toxic
OL,4,Cculture in the BBC
OL,6,FBBC Chair Dr Shah told staff today:
OL,7,F"There is a minority of people whose
OL,8,Fbehaviour is simply not acceptable.
OL,9,FAnd there are still places where
OL,10,Fpowerful individuals ` on and off
OL,11,Fscreen ` can abuse that power to make
OL,12,Flife for their colleagues unbearable.
OL,14,FHe added: "In the end, it's quite
OL,15,Fsimple: if you are a person who is
OL,16,Fprepared to abuse power or punch down
OL,17,For behave badly, there is no place for
OL,18,Fyou at the BBC."
