OL,4,Cculture in the BBC
OL,6,FThe review, led by management
OL,7,Fconsultant Grahame Russell, was
OL,8,Flaunched in the wake of the furore
OL,9,Fover disgraced former newsreader Huw
OL,10,FEdwards and has ruled out the presence
OL,11,Fof a toxic culture but found that
OL,12,Fimprovements can be made.
OL,14,FThe review, on "preventing abuse of
OL,15,Fpower and ensuring everyone at the BBC
OL,16,Fconducts themselves in line" with its
OL,17,Fvalues, has also set out what the
OL,18,Fcorporation expects from staff.
